text: Patella natalensis is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Patellidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== * Ridgway T.M., Branch G.M., Stewart B.A. (1999). Patella natalensis Krauss, 1848: re- description of an unrecognized limpet from the east coast of South Africa. Journal of Molluscan Studies 65:139–142. Category:Patellidae Category:Gastropods described in 1848 Category:Taxa named by Christian Ferdinand Friedrich Krauss
title: Patella natalensis
